thread.title: Palm Beach Notches Big-Ticket Home Sales

author: WSJ Real Estate
title: Palm Beach Notches Big-Ticket Home Sales
text:
MANSION Palm Beach Notches Big-Ticket Home Sales Palm Beach has made headlines lately not only because of frequent presidential visits, but because of an unusually high number of big-ticket home sales. The flurry of mega-sales may be due, in part, to the publicity Palm Beach has received during the president’s visits. But residents say these large deals also might stem from a broader sea change emerging in the area.
